{{Otheruses|Edge}}
'''Edge-9''' was an anarchist organization that existed on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It called for the dismantlement of Coruscant's government and the abolition of the gentry. It was known for its violent acts of political protest, though not all members explicitly supported violence. Edge-9's acts included [[Bomb/Legends|bombings]] of [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|police]] and utility stations. Anarchists from Edge-9 at one point plotted to destroy the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]], sneaking explosives through the pipeline from the polar caps, but the plot was foiled.

[[Reina March]] was a head [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] in the organization who planned and participated in violent acts. The organization existed even during the days of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], but its membership was much smaller and more fanatical.

